      • initialize

        public static int initialize(AsyncTask<?,Integer,?> task,
                             Context context)
        Initialize Metaio Cloud Plugin.

        This should be called once in the application inside AsyncTask.

        Returns:
        one of the error codes, i.e. SUCCESS CANCELLED ERROR_EXSTORAGE ERROR_INSTORAGE ERROR_NETWORK ERROR_GOOGLE_SERVICES ERROR_CPU_NOT_SUPPORTED

      • openURL

        public static boolean openURL(Activity activity,
                              String url,
                              boolean external,
                              boolean navigation)
        Open specified URL in custom or default web browser

        It also handles URIs with protocols mailto:, tel:, sms:, geo: and market://. All URIs are opened in an external application.

        Parameters:
        activity - Activity context
        url - URL or URI
        external - if URL should be opened in default external browser, or custom browser
        navigation - if navigation buttons should be visible in custom browser
        Returns:
        true on success, false on failure
